{"tid":1518413,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"特首，請拿起你的尚方寶劍","createTime":"2019-08-30T08:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T09:21:50.000Z","uid":314491,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8302c5f222705a1ff289502189b2eb40633edec8","tid":1518413,"uid":314491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:50:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://external-lga3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/safe_image.php?d=AQAIU99u79p79fqA&amp;w=540&amp;h=282&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgpao.com%2Fimg%2F2019%2F08%2F20190829_20190829-qu.blog.jpg&amp;cfs=1&amp;upscale=1&amp;fallback=news_d_placeholder_publisher&amp;_nc_hash=AQDIV2McGQr2UW3N\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexternal-lga3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fsafe_image.php%3Fd%3DAQAIU99u79p79fqA%26w%3D540%26h%3D282%26url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.hkgpao.com%252Fimg%252F2019%252F08%252F20190829_20190829-qu.blog.jpg%26cfs%3D1%26upscale%3D1%26fallback%3Dnews_d_placeholder_publisher%26_nc_hash%3DAQDIV2McGQr2UW3N&h=337214e0&s={SIZE}\" />\u0002\u0002\u0002日前明珠台《清心直說》（Straight Talk）節目訪問參與暴動的中大學生呂天忻，她說，年輕人要求特首林鄭「特赦被捕人士」，是因為「專業顧問和教授告訴他們，林鄭有《基本法》賦予的權力，可以把被捕者全部釋放。」即使主持人多次反駁：「一放人就是破壞法治」，呂同學仍堅持，「專業顧問和教授」說可以的。<br />\n<br />\n　　終於有人說出來了，學生背後，一直有一班教唆犯罪的人。<br />\n<br />\n　　「專業顧問和教授」，我們姑且理解為律師、大狀、議員和大學教師，說老實，兩個多月來，這班教唆犯罪者，已不避嫌地露出頭來指點江山。<br />\n<br />\n　　既然孩子們相信權威，既然權威告訴學生「特首可以用特權特赦罪犯」，那我也想提出我的訴求，就是懇請林鄭動用特首的尚方寶劍，引用「緊急法」為香港止暴制亂、為小島止血救民。<br />\n<br />\n　　孩子們，請去問問你們的「專業顧問和教授」，去翻翻香港法例第二百四十一章《緊急情況規例條例》，那裏白紙黑字寫明，只要特首會同行政會議認為社會屬緊急狀況或危害公安時，就可繞過立法會，在短時間內訂立任何合乎公眾利益並有法律效力的規則。<br />\n<br />\n　　例一，立即訂立禁蒙面法，此例一出，我相信出來衝擊的黑衣人將沒了八成，或者更多。<br />\n<br />\n&emsp;&emsp;例二，立即堵截暴徒的通訊系統，中止Telegram、連登等網絡程式。<br />\n<br />\n　　例三，禁止在警署、機場、港鐵、公路、隧道等地方聚集，讓社會回復正常運作。<br />\n<br />\n　　例四，賦予警方更大權力追查暴徒幕後主腦、資金來源、物資供應鏈等，源頭打擊。<br />\n<br />\n　　例子太多，不能盡錄，但這條緊急法，是孩子們你們最喜歡也最相信的英國人訂立的，六十年代英國殖民者曾經用過，去年颱風「山竹」襲港，立法會法律界議員郭榮鏗也曾要求特首出動此緊急法例，把打風翌日訂為公眾假期。<br />\n<br />\n　　既然打風後的亂狀都可以用，我想不到反對派的專業人士今日有甚麼理由反對，畢竟，今日香港的混亂及蕭條，傷害之入骨程度，比起「山竹」，豈只萬倍。<br />\n<br />\n屈穎妍"},{"pid":"ecb8aea79d83b4da649d516aa98661f0afebe09b","tid":1518413,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:51:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2C0Wvub.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2C0Wvub.gif&h=e09262cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiiC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=83af9e52\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiiC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=eaafcbfe\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUiiC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=1daf263b\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"501de0af9c43e21ca1ac1b12cce5102c8464b94a","tid":1518413,"uid":140326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dFMnydY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdFMnydY.png&h=4dee6fb5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"330aeb63b7a8976303b066e1ca39b6c6db4a08fd","tid":1518413,"uid":264457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:53:17.000Z","msg":"我地都支持特權法架。唔好屈我地唔支持呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39795929170a50b7543bedc598126ccdd1fc6364","tid":1518413,"uid":194298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:53:39.000Z","msg":"有時